{"tid":2282923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"捐錢捐到我份身家無曬","createTime":"2020-11-12T07:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T11:34:19.000Z","uid":217822,"like":27,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a464dffea7db6a610133904938845647ce050961","tid":2282923,"uid":217822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"因為我係有良知嘅深黃手足所以捐錢已經成為我生活一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期一:捐俾612($100)<br />\n(雖然法治已死，但係都要打官司)<br />\n<br />\n星期二:捐俾攬炒巴($100)<br />\n(雖然攬炒巴係外國人，同埋到依家都唔知佢做左啲咩但係香港人都係要科金俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為這是我們的職責!)<br />\n<br />\n星期三:捐俾泛民($200)<br />\n(雖然議會戰線已經失敗左，但係鄺神仲要供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n星期四:捐俾龍門渣哥($200)<br />\n(龍門好難食，所以小捐錢算)<br />\n(雖然渣哥開係地鐵站，但佢之前投票事件令香港人充分理解到偽民主嘅可怕，為港人上左寶貴嘅一堂，所以反唔落)<br />\n<br />\n星期五:捐俾媽咪麵(散銀)<br />\n(雖然係大陸牛牛資深用家生cancer都仲浪費時間上連登，但係我深黃有良知，所以照捐)<br />\n<br />\n平時早午晚都食黃店一日300(黃店平均100蚊一餐)<br />\n未計日日都要落樓下買屈臣水(擺用東江水)<br />\n<br />\n唔計六日 一個禮拜已經要用二千幾蚊<br />\n想知其他手足點捱，指點下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b84c09013550a952fe8e3717c144b490f2d5f4","tid":2282923,"uid":58617,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"量力而為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa26cb17139c4bee80112592300096518563d27","tid":2282923,"uid":178382,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"每月都捐比中大email<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(雖然佢好肥，但佢深黃+我要打丁)"},{"pid":"da6d6c5d3ec79ba028e51d5f21b20097b4fbea06","tid":2282923,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63374c55127635daa13b10013c37b93fba250ff3","tid":2282923,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲慈善過慈善球王"},{"pid":"44c11b471f730be503b2368036f4d01e1c554eea","tid":2282923,"uid":23655,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"我做哂樓主啲嘢<br />\n再加每個月課金比深黃手足email同miss pun<br />\n月月入不敷出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f02d4b6511ff5fc233720f7bd51378cea995fd","tid":2282923,"uid":3454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"44c11b471f730be503b2368036f4d01e1c554eea","tid":2282923,"uid":23655,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"我做哂樓主啲嘢<br />\n再加每個月課金比深黃手足email同miss pun<br />\n月月入不敷出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"你仲要捐埋精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94648c3473b556c08cc22f41ae74475d890f60c2","tid":2282923,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58f02d4b6511ff5fc233720f7bd51378cea995fd","tid":2282923,"uid":3454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"44c11b471f730be503b2368036f4d01e1c554eea","tid":2282923,"uid":23655,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"我做哂樓主啲嘢<br />\n再加每個月課金比深黃手足email同miss pun<br />\n月月入不敷出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"你仲要捐埋精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:57:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲無計嘅<br />\n主要係食住都有問題"},{"pid":"ba8923275bd3b75bf1ab4263be4a214b384c4377","tid":2282923,"uid":343401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58f02d4b6511ff5fc233720f7bd51378cea995fd","tid":2282923,"uid":3454,"like":5,"dislike":0